[With this report Colombia officially confirms the presence of porcine epidemic diarrhea virus (PEDv) in its territory. See TG's commentaries in ProMED-mail archive no 20140319.2341300.

Colombia becomes the 1st country in South America to report PEDv to the OIE as an "emerging disease". - Mod.CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2532426,16.]
